title: r/Maliciouscompliance "I CHEATED ON YOU, SO GIVE ME YOUR CAR!"
description: r/Maliciouscompliance The lady in today's video cheats on her husband, and then expects her husband to just hand over his car while he continues to make payments on it! Their conflict come to a peak when the wife demands that OP comes to pick up all of his stuff. Malicious compliance activated! I guess that means the car too, sweetheart!
